name: Vs. Dave and Bambi: From Around The Web

description:
Wow this mod is quite an obscure one. The mod was almost lost but luckily wayback had my back. This mod was made by SergiollSayab666 and he lost the mod so this is pretty much for him.

Songs:

Pretty much the songs from 2.5 and 2.0

8-28-63 Cover (Choome Zafyah)

Bloodshed Cover (Choome Zafyah)

Kalampokiphobia (TPTF, Hellscape)

Nomophobia (TPTF, Hellscape)

Nonsense Cover (normalbasics98)

Run Cover (i forgor)

Sporting Cover (Ikaens)

Og Description:

12 Year Old Me saying I should make this so people can play they're remixes / mods ecc. in just one mod. Dave & Bambi are originally from MoldyGH, I'm not taking other mods and put them here to steal their work. Just for fun.
This mod will be updated again and again till im dead lol.

Hope you enjoy
